I am looking forward to presenting in an hour or so on &ldquo;How Identity Management Impacts the bottom line.&rdquo;
Yesterday I had fun delivering a session on &ldquo;ADFS vs Password Sync? It depends&rdquo; This morning Alex Simons of Microsoft revealed a few new things that change some of my advice.
Soon Azure AD can do the location restriction by application for SSO. This potentially eliminates a deal breaker for some people You can now run Password Sync and ADFS at the same time.
